# PolyFilm — Environment Variables
#
# GOOD NEWS: This app requires NO API keys.
# Both Polymarket (gamma-api.polymarket.com) and Kalshi (external-api.kalshi.com)
# expose public endpoints that do not require authentication.
#
# Nothing to configure in Vercel's Environment Variables panel —
# just deploy and it works.
#
# If you add private integrations in the future (e.g. Kalshi trading API,
# a database, or analytics), add them here with placeholder values so
# teammates know what to set in their own .env.local:
#
# KALSHI_API_KEY=your_kalshi_api_key_here
# DATABASE_URL=your_database_url_here
